('c1000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000004', 'b1000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000001', 4, 'fill_blank', '[Complete the summary. Choose from: Mexicans / random / rotating / despite / preserve / realising / sunlight / lacking / heavenly / percussion / chance / friction / unaware / without / make / heating / Eskimos / surprised / until / smoke] The first methods involved creating ___ (4)', 'friction', 1),
