('c1000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000008', 'b1000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000001', 8, 'fill_blank', '[Complete the summary. Choose from: Mexicans / random / rotating / despite / preserve / realising / sunlight / lacking / heavenly / percussion / chance / friction / unaware / without / make / heating / Eskimos / surprised / until / smoke] Continued until the 1850s ___ (8) the discovery of phosphorus.', 'despite', 1),
